title: Ijiranaide, Nagatoro-san (Don't Toy with Me, Miss Nagatoro)
synopsis: Every day, Naoto Hachiouji is teased relentlessly by Hayase Nagatoro, a first year student he meets one day in the library while working on his manga. After reading his story and seeing his awkward demeanor, she decides from that moment on to toy with him, even calling him "Senpai" in lieu of using his real name.
